What an experience to go through to be able to work with grains sent to us from breeders of WSU. Connection made by @culinarybreedingnetwork 🙌. Also a special thanks to @nicappuccitti and Tissa of @taborbread  for allowing us to use the mill. Greatful for the Baking community in the 🌲PNW🌲. EVENT IS BETWEEN 3-6 IF ATTENDING COME TASTE WHAT WE'VE MADE AND CHECK OUT WHAT ALL THE CHEFS OF PORTLAND WHIPPED UP FOR YOU!

#communitynotcompetition #whlolegrains #wholegrainbread #spelt#dinkelbrot#freshmilled

Next Pizza Night, Sunday 2/23. This time we’re bringing our good friends at @mill_a_cider, they’ll set up shop for a tasting of their epic boozy cider.  Enjoy while dining in, or grab a 4pack with your pizza to-go!  Doors open at 5pm sharp

Put it in your calendar! February 16th you can catch us at the @reddonsalmon nerding out about grain with other food nerds for the Variety Showcase put on by the lovelies at @culinarybreedingnetwork. So many cool folks in attendance, what an event it will be!

Thinking of you..✌️✌🏾✌🏿✌🏽✌🏻✌️✌🏾✌🏿✌🏻

and just like that it’s 2020. We’re back open and slinging bread. Come be our first customer of the new year!

#freegrain #wholehrain #breadwithoutborders
Open all weekend with a bunch of these babka babes #babkadaze
It’s Sunday, which means its pizza night! Come for a pastry this morning, come back for a pizza later tonight - we’ve got you covered all day today. Doors reopen at 5

Gifts in the mail courtesy of our friends @wsu_bread_lab - Elwha River Spelt. So stoked to start playing with this for the Variety Showcase next year. Shout out to @culinarybreedingnetwork and all the grain nerds out there who bring makers/bakers and growers/tinkerers together to make good food happen. #grainbow #wholegrainbread #sourdoughlife

Special hours for the holidays. We will be open Monday 12/23 7am to 4pm for all the bread, treats and pre order pick ups. We’ll be open Tuesday 12/24 for a half day, 7am to Noon! We’ll be closed 12/25 through 1/1 to celebrate the holidays with our families.
We’re sneaking in 1 more pizza night before the end of the year. Sunday 12/15, 5-8:30pm, menu coming soon
While you were sleeping 💤 we’re ready for the crowds - pies - rolls and all the bread!

Last day for thanksgiving pre orders! But don’t fret, we’ll have extras of everything available Tuesday and Wednesday (rolls and pies) to help with those last minute dinner guests #wholegrain #thanksgiving #surpriseguest
